               <msContents>
                  <summary>Miniature Codex of Prayer against the Tongue of People, ልሳነ፡ ሰብእ፡, Asmat Prayers</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="19r" facs="002">Fols 1r–19r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3034RepCh314">Hymn to Jesus
                                                  Christ</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="19r" to="20r" facs="020">Fols 19r–20r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer against fear and nightmare, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎተ፡ ድንጋፄ፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎተ፡ ድንጋጼ፡ ዘወሀቦ፡ እግዚእ፡ ለአዳም፡ አመ፡ ወጽአ፡ እምገነት፡ ወይቤ፡ ሎ፡ ፌያም፡ ብልሰቅያም፡ ኵልዛዛሄር፡ ብያም፡ ርባርዮስ፡ በዝ፡ አስማተ፡ ላህ፡ እምድንጋጼ፡ ባርያ፡ ወሌጌዎን፡</incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <locus from="20r" to="22v" facs="021">Fols 20r–22v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5690MagicPrayer">Ṣalot baʾǝnta
                                                  ʿayna ṭǝlā wa-ʿayna warq ṣelota nədrā zəwəʾǝtu
                                                  ḥǝmāma ʿayna ʾəkkuy<foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ንድራ፡</foreign></title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ንድራ፡ ዝውእቱ፡ ዓይነት፡ ወዓይነ፡ ወርቅ፡ ወእንዘ፡ የሐውር፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ውስተ፡ ባህረ፡ ጥብርያዶስ፡ ወምስሌሁ፡ ፲ወ፪ አርዳኢሁ፡ ወርእዩ፡ መልክዓ፡ ብእሲት፡ ዓረጊት፡ እንዘ፡ ትነብር፡ መልዕልተ፡ ዖም፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <locus from="22v" to="23v" facs="024">Fols 22v–23v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat Prayer against Arthritis, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ቁርጥማት፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ቁርጥማት፡ ሸምዳን ተክለ፡ ሸርታን፡ ሐገሌ፡ ዘጌጓዘጌዘጌ፡ ይኩን፡ ብከ፡ ማኅተመ፡ ንጉሥከ፡ ወዋከያ፡ ወዘወለተ፡ ወርቅ፡ ንግሥትከ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                     <locus from="23v" to="24r" facs="025">Fols 23v–24r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat Prayer against Evil Eye (Buda), <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ ዘቁመኛ፡ ወቡዳ፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ ዘቁመኛ፡ ወቡዳ፡ ወዘይሰልብ፡ ልበ፡ ቤጣ[፡] የውጣ[፡] አማኑኤል፡ [፡]ትስቡጣ<gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
